OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with clear periods. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will remain dry
OL,8,Fwith variable amounts of cloud. Strong
OL,9,Fsoutherly winds developing along the
OL,10,FSolway coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FThe morning will be dry,
OL,13,Fsome hazy sunshine in the east. Rain
OL,14,Fwill gradually spread east across all
OL,15,Fparts through the afternoon and
OL,16,Fevening. Mild across the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
