OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA cold
OL,6,Fstart with some frost on Friday, then
OL,7,Fa dry and sunny day, Dry and bright on
OL,8,FSaturday, clouding over later. Cloudy
OL,9,Fwith a chance of rain on Sunday.
